Biography

2021 Season

Second on the team with 3 multi-RBI games ... hit 2-run homer in series finale vs UTSA (2/27) ... went 3-for-5 with 2 runs scored and an RBI in win over RIce (3/5) in opener of Shriners Hospitals for Children College Classic at Minute Maid Park ... delivered 2-run single in upset win over No. 13 TCU (3/7) ... also delivered 2-run single and scored a run at Southeastern Louisiana (3/13).

2020 Season

Started each of the first 6 games of the year at third base for the Bearkats, getting at least one hit in each game ... started 5-4-3 triple play in fourth inning vs Loyola Marymount (2/21), the second recorded triple play in Bearkat history ... play also landed at No. 7 on that night's ESPN Sports Center Top 10 countdown ... went 3-for-4 with a double and an RBI on Opening Night in a win over Saint Mary's (2/14) ... had a hit in each of the next 2 games, scoring once in series finale (2/16) ... also had a hand in 3 of school-record 6 double plays turned in Game 2 win vs the Gaels (2/15) ... went 2-for-4 with an RBI and 2 runs scored in Game 1 vs Loyola Marymount (2/21) ... went 2-for-2 with an RBI single against Houston Baptist (3/7).

Galveston College

Spent 2 seasons at Galveston College ... started as a catcher before moving to third base as a sophomore ... hit .320 with a homer and 36 RBI in 2019 ... also had 49 hits and 11 doubles ... finished with a .320/397/.412 slash line ... also stole 12 bases.

No stats available for the current season.
